OL,3,CPageantry and pleasantries but no new
OL,4,Cpolicy: Trump and Xi's summit
OL,6,FSeeds offered to US President Donald
OL,7,FTrump from Chinese President Xi
OL,8,FJinping's rose garden are likely the
OL,9,Fmost solid things he is taking back to
OL,10,Fthe States, reports ITV News' Asia
OL,11,FCorrespondent Debi Edward
OL,13,FStrategic stability may not provide
OL,14,Fthe sexiest of headlines, but that's
OL,15,Fthe top takeaway from a summit both
OL,16,Fthe US and China agreed was historic.
OL,18,FThis meeting had box office billing
OL,19,Fbut ended up being largely a reset in
OL,20,Frelations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
