OL,3,CPageantry and pleasantries but no new
OL,4,Cpolicy: Trump and Xi's summit
OL,6,FWe had two days packed with pageantry
OL,7,Fand pleasantries, but a lack of new
OL,8,Fpolicy.
OL,10,FThe seeds that Trump was offered from
OL,11,FXi Jinping's rose garden were probably
OL,12,Fthe most solid things he is taking
OL,13,Fback to the United States.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
