OL,3,CPageantry and pleasantries but no new
OL,4,Cpolicy: Trump and Xi's summit
OL,6,FThere were deals for China to buy
OL,7,Fbeef, Boeing planes, and soybeans, but
OL,8,Fthere were no major breakthroughs on
OL,9,Ftrade tariffs, tech, or Taiwan.
OL,11,FDiscussions are apparently ongoing
OL,12,Fabout establishing a Board of Trade or
OL,13,FInvestments.
OL,15,FOn Iran, President Trump claimed China
OL,16,Fhad agreed not to provide weapons to
OL,17,FTehran and help get a deal done to
OL,18,Fopen the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
