FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779030723
OL,3,CPageantry and pleasantries but no new
OL,4,Cpolicy: Trump and Xi's summit
OL,6,FThe Chinese readout of events didn't
OL,7,Fmention such specific promises, but
OL,8,Fdid offer to support the peace process.
OL,10,FThe Trump we saw in China didn't
OL,11,Fanswer reporters' questions; when they
OL,12,Fwere able to get close enough, there
OL,13,Fwere no press conferences, and there
OL,14,Fwas no running commentary on social
OL,15,Fmedia.
OL,17,FBut as soon as Air Force One was in
OL,18,Fthe smoggy skies of Beijing on its way
OL,19,Fback to the United States, normal
OL,20,Fservice resumed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
