OL,3,CPageantry and pleasantries but no new
OL,4,Cpolicy: Trump and Xi's summit
OL,6,FThe US president gave a lengthy,
OL,7,Funfiltered mid-air press briefing,
OL,8,Fwhere he took questions on everything
OL,9,Fthat had been discussed.
OL,11,FThe standout comments for those of us
OL,12,Fwho cover this region were what he
OL,13,Fsaid about Taiwan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
