OL,3,CPageantry and pleasantries but no new
OL,4,Cpolicy: Trump and Xi's summit
OL,6,FGoing into this meeting, there were
OL,7,Fconcerns that Trump would be convinced
OL,8,Fby Xi to end a long-established
OL,9,Fagreement to provide the island with
OL,10,Fweapons to defend itself, and that the
OL,11,FUS would change the language to
OL,12,Fsupport Beijing's position over
OL,13,FTaipei's.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
