PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779030723
OL,3,CPageantry and pleasantries but no new
OL,4,Cpolicy: Trump and Xi's summit
OL,6,FIt turns out that the two presidents
OL,7,Fdid discuss arms sales, and Trump said
OL,8,Fhe would make a decision on whether or
OL,9,Fnot to continue with an already
OL,10,Fplanned weapons sale in "the next
OL,11,Fshort period of time'' he said he
OL,12,Fwould be reaching out to the president
OL,13,Fof Taiwan to discuss the matter.
OL,15,FTrump said China didn't want a war,
OL,16,Fand he didn't want another one either;
OL,17,F"the last thing" he said they needed
OL,18,Fright now was a war 9,500 miles away.
OL,26,@rD@YOUyD@AOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
