PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779030723
OL,3,CPageantry and pleasantries but no new
OL,4,Cpolicy: Trump and Xi's summit
OL,6,FWhen asked if he would come to
OL,7,FTaiwan's defence in the event of a
OL,8,Fconfrontation, Trump declined to
OL,9,Fanswer and told reporters there was
OL,10,F''only one person who knows that, and
OL,11,Fyou know who it is, me."
OL,13,FThey were responses which will not
OL,14,Fhave filled the people of Taiwan with
OL,15,Fmuch confidence.
OL,17,FSo was the much-heralded Xi-Trump
OL,18,Fsummit a success?
OL,26,@sD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
