OL,3,CPageantry and pleasantries but no new
OL,4,Cpolicy: Trump and Xi's summit
OL,6,FIn the sense that nobody wants these
OL,7,Ftwo superpowers to be at war, it was a
OL,8,Fgood starting point for what we are
OL,9,Ftold will be a more cooperative than
OL,10,Fcompetitive era in US-China relations.
OL,12,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,13,Four political experts are across all
OL,14,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,15,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
